{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d80e954c42","title":"给毛月秋的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5fa7e08bc1","index":0,"year":1953,"month":10,"day":4,"articleId":"d80e954c42"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"abb4fbb86c","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛月秋，大革命时期曾在部山任中共慈悦支部书记。新中国成立后在韶山毛泽东旧居做过接待工作。"},{"id":"ed84e8529e","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛翼臣，是毛锡臣之误。毛锡臣是毛泽东的远房叔祖父。"},{"id":"4451e2144d","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"文东仙，毛泽东的表弟。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3585b3da03","type":"title","text":"给毛月秋的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"abb4fbb86c","type":"paragraph","text":"月秋同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"ed84e8529e","type":"paragraph","text":"你给我的信收到。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"4451e2144d","type":"paragraph","text":"为了了解乡间情况的目的（不是为了祝寿。为了节约，无论哪一年均不要祝寿，此点要讲清楚），我同意你来京一行。尚有毛翼臣（不知住什么地方）、文东仙（唐家坪）二同志过去来信，表示要来我处一看。如你及乡间其他同志同意的话，你可约同他们二位一道来京。除你们三人外，其他没有预先约好的同志，一概不要来。你们到京住一个短期仍回家乡。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"a42741fbc7","type":"paragraph","text":"你们来时，即持此信先到长沙湖南省委统一战线部，找那里的同志帮忙，发给你们三人来京的路费，并请他们派一人送你们来京。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"4bbeb0e159","type":"paragraph","text":"另请你持此信，到韶山、石城两处乡政府及当地的两个区政府及党的负责同志处，和他们商量，如果他们同意的话，请他们将两乡两区的情况及追切需要解决的困难问题，写成书面材料，交你带来，作为参考之用（不是为了直接解决乡间问题）。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"2dccfc0255","type":"paragraph","text":"你们三人来时，不要带任何礼物。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"bdbc6e39a8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们到京时间，以早为好，希望不退于阳历十月二十日至二十五日。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"81ab3fb63f","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"1e0635b192","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"},{"id":"a3b46d5917","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年十月四日","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42"}],"page":{"id":"e73d90eb56","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d80e954c42","start":372,"end":373}}}},"__N_SSG":true}